11️⃣ HOT–WARM–COLD STRATEGY
HOT
Active runs + active sessions.
WARM
Completed runs (current academic year).
COLD
Past academic year:
    • Sessions exported to BigQuery
    • runAnalytics retained
    • Session collections optionally deleted from Firestore
    • Year marked archived
This prevents Firestore bloat.

12️⃣ SECURITY RULES
Assignment must enforce:
    • One active session per student per run
    • Server-authoritative timer
    • Window enforcement server-side
    • Signed session token
    • No direct exam link via email
    • Portal-based entry only
    • Session cannot change mode mid-run
    • Student cannot modify shuffle

13️⃣ SCORE NORMALIZATION RULE
Across Assignment module:
Always display:
    • Avg Raw Score %
    • Avg Accuracy %
Never display:
    • Raw marks
    • Total marks comparison
Normalization protects:
    • Chapter tests
    • Full mocks
    • Mixed difficulty tests

14️⃣ DESIGN PRINCIPLES
Assignment Section must:
